  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this post market clinical follow-up (PMCF) investigation is to
      evaluate performance and safety of Exufiber when used as intended in Stage II-IV pressure
      ulcers (PU).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
